main event: A civilian observed a bright, round unidentified aircraft in Albany, Oregon on 20 April 1966.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for only one minute,The object was moving very fast towards the south-southwest,There was another object trailing the main aircraft,The report was part of Project 10073,The object was bright white and one half the size of a dive.
sighted object: one round, bright white unidentified aircraft
